    list TnlAssociation {
      description "Additional definitions from MOM:min/max-elements:0/32;systemCreated; Transport Network Layer association between gNodeB and AMF. Created when new SCTP association is successfully established between gNodeB and AMF. Deleted when SCTP association removal is ordered by AMF or when NG-C connection between gNodeB and AMF is released. The RDN of this MO is TnlAssociation=[Remote Port]_[Remote IP]. Example: TnlAssociation=38412_2001:0db8:85a3:0000:0000:8a2e:0370:7334. Length of RDN value is up to 45 characters. Instance can be created without a preceding user-initiated transaction.";
